This plugin uses Dropbox PHP client library from : http://code.google.com/p/dropbox-php/
and for Authentication to work...
You should install OAuth php extension on the Apache2 server
using "pecl install oauth" command. and restarted the Apache2 server.

You can always download the sources, compile and install it.
http://pecl.php.net/package/oauth
(Do not forget to add the proper extension=oauth.so line to the right php.ini)

Feedback and Support: nadavkav@gmail.com (Nadav Kavalerchik)

Enjoy :-)